  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">腾讯混元3D</span></span></span><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">开源</span></span></span><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">模型</span></span></span><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">又添新成员。</span></span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">6月14日，在计算机视觉领域国际顶级会议CVPR 2025上，腾讯混元3D 2.1大模型正式对外开源，这也是首个全链路开源的工业级3D生成大模型。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/498bc79b-80f5-42a7-2dde-e01bb911b700/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100011279\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/498bc79b-80f5-42a7-2dde-e01bb911b700/public\"></span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a6eb12c6-932c-48c0-f6d0-782359b0fb00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.721627408993576\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"934\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100011275\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a6eb12c6-932c-48c0-f6d0-782359b0fb00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">相较于广受社区欢迎的混元3D 2.0，2.1模型</span></span></span><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">优化</span></span></span><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">了</span></span></span><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">几何</span></span></span><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">生成</span></span></span><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">的</span></span></span><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">质量</span></span></span><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，</span></span></span><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">同时</span></span></span><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">开放</span></span></span><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">了</span></span></span><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">PBR（基于物理的渲染）</span></span></span><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">材质</span></span></span><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">生成</span></span></span><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">大模型</span></span></span><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，进一步提升3D资产的质感和光影表现，</span></span></span><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">将AI 3D开源模型的可用性推进至全链路</span></span></span><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">可用</span></span></span><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">阶段</span></span></span><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。</span></span></span><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:微软雅黑;font-style:normal;\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">腾讯混元3D模型负责人郭春超表示，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">混元3D 2.1的全面开源是一个新起点，期待与全球开发者、创作者及研究者携手，共同打造更加繁荣的3D开源生态</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。</span></span></span></p>\n  <section class=\"channels_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <mp-common-videosnap class=\"js_uneditable custom_select_card channels_iframe videosnap_video_iframe videosnap_video_iframe\" data-pluginname=\"mpvideosnap\" data-url=\"https://findermp.video.qq.com/251/20304/stodownload?encfilekey=rjD5jyTuFrIpZ2ibE8T7Ym3K77SEULgkiaDBdicERBWSmAVQ8RUPafCJNDiaNHtCrCAt5Oiak0Pgahg7X6tXSQ4eboOAwAsRj2XSBm2QLXmrJPgasvSGy88aT3w&amp;token=2lt8WBSnjTlaak46A8eYXbnibicOmiarXXwmjCSsNVibL53JiczdlmHqMEB1Niak3uX8nKSFuYnLcLJdicZXpBVCBLzKt9PlKdxLGkOvFGU1XxSr5J7ZCzQ3UMTBrsf73fstQ6XMQhILYpx9VcAiaXIGicGzPPwJAU0ic6uzLECKQt7HHCiaOI&amp;idx=1&amp;hy=SZ&amp;m=&amp;scene=2&amp;uzid=1\" data-headimgurl=\"http://wx.qlogo.cn/finderhead/Y3WgNLFjO0e1rbGnQDFTLKdL1uAeeMVqqicdyVkLBicfXdz04ecGicUxQ/0\" data-username=\"v2_060000231003b20faec8c6eb8f1fc3d6cb02e835b077d30f0f482bdbb4c0d99547aa16a4af80@finder\" data-nickname=\"腾讯混元\" data-desc=\"腾讯混元3D 2.1模型来了！模型权重、训练代码和数据处理流程全面开源，开放PBR（基于物理的渲染）材质生成大模型，进一步提升3D资产的质感和光影表现～ #腾讯混元 #腾讯混元3D #3D建模 #AIGC\n\" data-nonceid=\"5434232568905227724\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-type=\"video\" data-id=\"export/UzFfAgtgekIEAQAAAAAAeuUJuIvWFgAAAAstQy6ubaLX4KHWvLEZgBPExYJ4WldzGb-IzNPgMIv1C6B3VHySpoVGFDD0pA7X\"></mp-common-videosnap>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  <section style=\"font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <section style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <section style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;border-bottom: 3px solid rgb(6, 50, 253);padding-bottom: 3px;border-top-color: rgb(6, 50, 253);border-right-color: rgb(6, 50, 253);border-left-color: rgb(6, 50, 253);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <section style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(6, 50, 253);border-top-color: rgb(6, 50, 253);border-right-color: rgb(6, 50, 253);border-left-color: rgb(6, 50, 253);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">几何与纹理双优化，PBR技术提升真实感</span></span></strong></p>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n    <span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">如果说几何是3D模型的“骨骼”，定义了模型的形态、轮廓与细节精度；纹理则是3D模型的“皮肤”，还原模型表面的颜色、光泽和细节表现。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在混元3D 2.0的基础上，混元3D 2.1模型进一步强化了“几何-纹理解耦”架构。</span></span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b3bae8ce-655c-41be-7c21-2e8d90bdef00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8379629629629629\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" height=\"506.784\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;width: 604.733px;height: 506.784px;\" width=\"604.733\" data-imgfileid=\"100011252\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b3bae8ce-655c-41be-7c21-2e8d90bdef00/public\"></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">基于DiT几何架构，混元3D 2.1优化了细节建模，使网格精度更高，具备更好的</span></span></span><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">形状</span></span></span><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">一致性，为后续纹理映射提供了坚实的基础。</span></span></span><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">同时，混元率先在3D开源模型中引入PBR纹理生成技术。基于多视图生成、逆渲染和贴图技术，混元3D 2.1 可生成基础颜色、金属</span></span></span><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">度</span></span></span><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">、粗糙度等贴图，支持皮革、木质、金属、陶瓷等多种复杂材质的高质量渲染。</span></span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">相较传统RGB 贴图技术，PBR通过模拟光线与材质的物理交互，提升模型在不同光照环境下的视觉一致性。在用户盲测中，混元3D 2.1的PBR纹理相较于RGB贴图，质感胜出率高达78%。</span></span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2730060b-2a5f-45ad-bcdc-8eea61504900/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100011282\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2730060b-2a5f-45ad-bcdc-8eea61504900/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/edfb0bce-bb50-46d8-8638-c0308bbe4d00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5625579240037072\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1079\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100011259\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/edfb0bce-bb50-46d8-8638-c0308bbe4d00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这种物理真实性不仅满足电影、游戏等高要求渲染场景的需求，也为工业设计、虚拟仿真和数字孪生提供了可靠3D资产。此外，PBR材质的标准化特性使其兼容主流渲染引擎（如Unreal Engine、Unity），提高了3D资产在跨平台、跨行业的复用性，推动3D模型从消费级创作向工业级应用的转型。</span></span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  <section style=\"font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <section style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <section style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;border-bottom: 3px solid rgb(6, 50, 253);padding-bottom: 3px;border-top-color: rgb(6, 50, 253);border-right-color: rgb(6, 50, 253);border-left-color: rgb(6, 50, 253);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <section style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(6, 50, 253);border-top-color: rgb(6, 50, 253);border-right-color: rgb(6, 50, 253);border-left-color: rgb(6, 50, 253);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">全链路开源，降低开发门槛</span></span></strong></p>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n    <span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">混元3D 2.1大模型在效果全面升级的基础上，提供了模型权重、训练代码和数据处理流程的全链路开源，开发者可以自由微调、二次训练或优化，满足定制化需求，同时为学术研究提供平台。</span></span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在部署方面，混元3D 2.1适配于消费级显卡</span></span></span><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，在Github 等开源地址提供了详细部署和使用教程，企业、中小团队及个人开发者都能轻松上手。</span></span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">据悉，</span></span></span><span data-font-family=\"&quot;微软雅黑&quot;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">腾讯游戏自研编辑器</span></span></span><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">轻游梦工坊已应用混元 3D在多条美术管线完成提效，道具管线制作周期由2天/个降低至0.2天/个，相信模型</span></span></span><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">开源有望加速3D内容创作的普及。</span></span></span></p>\n  <section nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <iframe class=\"video_iframe rich_pages\" data-src=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/readtemplate?t=pages/video_player_tmpl&amp;action=mpvideo&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=wxv_4030456172942458895\" data-mpvid=\"wxv_4030456172942458895\" data-vidtype=\"2\" data-cover=\"http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F9u3YmmgmjbQphUYlnq87qgf67d8oWCDZDia8wicV69GhXOYABic6eicGkfeFPSNNlXzEMfD7Heo6iaCgMuzzWsNHjvA%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></iframe>\n  </section>\n  <section nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <iframe class=\"video_iframe rich_pages\" data-src=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/readtemplate?t=pages/video_player_tmpl&amp;action=mpvideo&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=wxv_4030457581507100672\" data-mpvid=\"wxv_4030457581507100672\" data-vidtype=\"2\" data-cover=\"http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F9u3YmmgmjbQphUYlnq87qgf67d8oWCDZtvmlM0KOnGBict39vWZ8ajLIC83SyC13rDKO8jwNYJvrHv7eR2Dz6Bw%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></iframe>\n  </section>\n  <section nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <iframe class=\"video_iframe rich_pages\" data-src=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/readtemplate?t=pages/video_player_tmpl&amp;action=mpvideo&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=wxv_4030458965577089028\" data-mpvid=\"wxv_4030458965577089028\" data-vidtype=\"2\" data-cover=\"http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F9u3YmmgmjbQphUYlnq87qgf67d8oWCDZ6ibXwC8vL7oaeyNfTj1o0ynQHClb9VDKbNVu1lA8hbZsOHHg0lAoTCA%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></iframe>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <section style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <section style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;border-bottom: 3px solid rgb(6, 50, 253);padding-bottom: 3px;border-top-color: rgb(6, 50, 253);border-right-color: rgb(6, 50, 253);border-left-color: rgb(6, 50, 253);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <section style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(6, 50, 253);border-top-color: rgb(6, 50, 253);border-right-color: rgb(6, 50, 253);border-left-color: rgb(6, 50, 253);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">持续突破，助力开源生态繁荣</span></span></strong></p>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section>\n    <span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">腾讯混元3D致力于通过AIGC技术重塑3D制作管线，致力于解决传统3D建模耗时、成本高、数据稀缺等行业痛点。</span></span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">自2024年11月发布并开源首代3D生成模型以来，腾讯混元持续迭代创新。2025年1月，混元3D 2.0在文本一致性与几何精度上超越主流模型；3月，一次性开源5款3D生成模型，实现秒级资产生成；</span></span></span><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">4</span></span></span><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">月，混元3D 2.5模型精度提升超10倍，迈入超高清时代。</span></span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">此前，腾讯还发布了面向创作者的3D AI创作引擎。该引擎支持文生、图生以及多视图输入功能</span></span></span><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，</span></span></span><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">同时具备智能</span></span></span><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">拓扑</span></span></span><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">能力——通过自回归技术生成拓扑结构接近手工布线的低模， 并整合了多套适配3D设计师需求的专业工作流，涵盖角色/道具设计等场景，可充分满足游戏开发、动画影视及3D打印等领域的专业需求。</span></span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5b38d1a4-bc98-4519-6185-9d297b6a3700/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3074074074074074\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" height=\"185.754\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;width: 604.733px;height: 185.754px;\" width=\"604.733\" data-imgfileid=\"100011251\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5b38d1a4-bc98-4519-6185-9d297b6a3700/public\"></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">腾讯混元坚定拥抱开源，旗下图像、视频、3D、文本等多种模态基础模型已全面开源。作为最受欢迎的 3D 开源模型之一，混元3D模型在Hugging Face平台下载量已超过180万，广受全球开发者认可。</span></span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\"></ul>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: normal;\">开源主页：https://3d-models.hunyuan.tencent.com/&nbsp;</span></span></p></li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: normal;\">Model: https://huggingface.co/tencent/Hunyuan3D-2.1</span></span></p></li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: normal;\">Demo: https://huggingface.co/spaces/tencent/Hunyuan3D-2.1</span></span></p></li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: normal;\">代码（Github）: https://github.com/Tencent-Hunyuan/Hunyuan3D-2.1</span></span></p></li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: normal;\">混元3D AI创作引擎: https://3d.hunyuan.tencent.com/</span></span></p></li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"line-height:1em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:8px;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height:1em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:8px;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">想玩转腾讯混元3D2.1，周日来直播间，这里有手把手教学👇</span></span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5be2805b-45c5-4481-0868-b95289bb7700/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.77734375\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100011258\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5be2805b-45c5-4481-0868-b95289bb7700/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section class=\"channels_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <mp-common-videosnap class=\"js_uneditable custom_select_card channels_live_iframe\" data-pluginname=\"mpvideosnap\" data-headimgurl=\"https://wx.qlogo.cn/finderhead/Y3WgNLFjO0e1rbGnQDFTLKdL1uAeeMVqqicdyVkLBicfXdz04ecGicUxQ/0\" data-username=\"v2_060000231003b20faec8c6eb8f1fc3d6cb02e835b077d30f0f482bdbb4c0d99547aa16a4af80@finder\" data-nickname=\"腾讯混元\" data-desc=\"将在06月15日 11:00 直播\" data-type=\"live\" data-intro=\"玩转混元3D 2.1\" data-noticeid=\"finderlivenotice-v2_060000231003b20faec8c6eb8f1fc3d6cb02e835b077d30f0f482bdbb4c0d99547aa16a4af80@finder-1749742395321060-114958852\" data-status=\"0\"></mp-common-videosnap>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "腾讯混元 3D 2.1 全链路开源，提升几何精度与 PBR 材质真实感。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "腾讯混元 3D 2.1 全链路开源，提升几何精度与 PBR 材质真实感。",
  "summary": "文章宣布腾讯混元在 CVPR 2025 会议上开源了混元 3D 2.1 大模型，这是首个全链路开源的工业级 3D 生成模型。相比 2.0 版本，2.1 模型在几何生成质量上有所优化，并率先在开源模型中引入 PBR（基于物理的渲染）材质生成技术，显著提升了 3D 资产的质感和跨平台兼容性。文章详细介绍了几何与纹理优化的技术细节，特别是 PBR 纹理如何通过模拟物理交互提升真实感，及其在工业级应用的潜力。此外，模型提供了包括模型权重、训练代码、数据处理流程在内的全链路开源，降低了开发者门槛，并适配消费级显卡。文章还提及了腾讯混元在 3D 生成领域的持续迭代，以及其模型在社区的受欢迎程度。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "腾讯混元 3D 2.1 作为首个全链路开源工业级模型发布",
      "explanation": "在 CVPR 2025 上宣布，提供从模型到训练、部署的全套资源，极大降低了 3D 生成技术的使用和研究门槛。"
    },
    {
      "point": "模型在几何生成和材质真实感上取得显著提升",
      "explanation": "通过优化 DiT 几何架构提升细节精度，并率先引入 PBR 纹理生成，使得 3D 资产视觉效果更真实，兼容性更强。"
    },
    {
      "point": "适配消费级显卡，助力技术普及和应用",
      "explanation": "较低的硬件要求使得更多企业、团队及个人开发者能够轻松部署和应用该模型，加速 3D 内容创作普及。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
